It is designed to provision, configure, and manage virtual machines and services in a reproducible and automated way.

## Goals

- Maintain a fully automated and reproducible homelab environment.
- Keep infrastructure and configuration version-controlled.
- Experiment with DevOps practices including IaC, CI/CD, and automated provisioning.
- Ensure modular, organized, and maintainable code.
